Your CANIVORE CAN bus - is it terminated?

Do you have RIO CAN that is terminated, even if it’s not used?

So, with some older versions we had issues similar to yours either when CANIVORE CAN was not properly terminated, or when RIO CAN was not terminated, even if there were no devices on it.
